<div class="compactUpload">
  <div action='post' id="signCompact">
      <div class='uploadWrapper'>
        <label><i>*</i>上传合同：</label>
        <span class="fileinput-button btn_upload">
            <i class="icon_upload"></i>
            <span>点击上传</span>
            <input id='fileupload' data-url='/api/upload-file' type="file" name="files">
        </span>
        <div id="files">
          <p class="file">aaa.png<span class="del"></span><input type="hidden" name="filepath" value="1"></p><p class="file">bbb.jpg<span class="del"></span><input type="hidden" name="filepath" value="2"></p><p class="file">ccc.gif<span class="del"></span><input type="hidden" name="filepath" value="3"></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='tip'>
        <label>提示：</label>
        <ul>
          <li>1. 请在<span>24小时内</span>下载合同，并加盖合同章或者公章后将合同扫描件或照片上传</li>
          <li>2. 请选择文件扫描件、照片、或文件压缩包上传，容量最大<span>不超过30M</span>。</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <input type="hidden" name="orderid" value="<%= orderid %>"/>
      <input type="hidden" name="action" value="post">
      <input type="button" class='cancel btn_gray' value="取消" data-toggle='modal' data-target='#cancelSignModel'/>
      <input type="button" class='submit btn_blue' value="确认提交" />
  </div>
  <div id="cancelSignModel" class="modal fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-header">
      <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">×</button>
      <h3>Modal header</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
      <p>确定取消签订合同？</p>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-footer">
      <button class="btn" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">取消</button>
      <a href='/orders' class="btn btn-primary">确认</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
